<DATE>
<P>
February 11, 1989, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 7; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
68 words 
