San Diego 93, St. Augustine 57 -- Milton Miller's 24-point effort led San Diego 
over visiting St. Augustine, and improved to 15-4, 6-2. St. Augustine's Mossuto 
brothers, Mike and Paul, scored 23 and 15 points. The Saints dropped to 2-18, 
1-7. Clark James and Raynard Wells added 18 and 11 points for San Diego. 
</P>
